# HTML Guidelines

## Structure and Semantics
- Use semantic HTML5 elements (`<header>`, `<section>`, `<main>`)
- Always include proper meta tags for SEO and social sharing
- Maintain German language content (`lang="de"`)
- Include Open Graph and Twitter Card meta tags
- Use proper heading hierarchy (h1, h2, etc.)

## Accessibility
- Include `aria-label` attributes for interactive elements
- Use `rel="noopener noreferrer"` for external links
- Ensure proper alt text for images
- Maintain focus states for keyboard navigation

## Content Guidelines
- Keep personal information in German
- Profile section should be centered and prominent
- Social links should be easily accessible
- Maintain professional tone throughout

## Meta Tags Required
- Title, description, keywords
- Open Graph tags (og:type, og:url, og:title, og:description, og:image)
- Twitter Card tags
- Canonical URL
- Theme color and viewport settings